## 1. Summary

| Ending | Reachable | Earn-gated | Stumble-in available |
|--------|-----------|------------|----------------------|
| Cure   | Yes       | No         | Yes                  |
| Weapon | Yes       | No         | Yes                  |
| Seal   | Yes       | No         | Yes                  |
| Throne | Yes       | No         | Yes                  |

**Key finding:** The DC 4 lore `skillCheck` on each terminal is flavor, not enforcement. The `questFlagOnSuccess` array fires regardless of whether the skill roll succeeds or fails (no `failNode` prevents flag-setting). All four endings are structurally reachable with zero quest investment once `cycleGate: 3` is satisfied.

